{"tid":2393640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主派總辭　改議事規則變「特辣」　響鐘點人數要問過主席","createTime":"2021-02-03T14:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T15:17:47.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b27a72e5e33799c24e4f8e26aa5b934296511106","tid":2393640,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:42:22.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n【Now新聞台】民主派總辭後，「拉布」場面已不再，但建制派繼續高唱「我們要反拉布」，提出修改議事規則。<br />\n北京去年宣布立法會續任後，建制派已醞釀修改議事規則，但一度「雷聲大雨點小」，只在內會修改內務守則。消息指，當時議會仍有民主派，擔心大動作會惹爭議，但隨著民主派總辭，有關方面認為機不可失，決定一不做二不休，徹底根治拉布問題。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=422832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D422832&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjR1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=392b0ad2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D422832&h=4ba01de0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=422832</a>"},{"pid":"cfed03045f2f124df8618209aeeafebb7cbb2c61","tid":2393640,"uid":231480,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:43:19.000Z","msg":"你哋玩飽佢"},{"pid":"6a1700938363670383f319638c7531b75bdcd554","tid":2393640,"uid":125168,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:44:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4ba0e411f289ec538a8d600d40a3aeb24b79391","tid":2393640,"uid":383914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cadbeffb6080bb94b1e8e9400ef1191a305b9faf","tid":2393640,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:45:08.000Z","msg":"你鍾意點咪點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.